description: It's In The Sauce BBQ is a mobile eatery in the Los Angeles area. Their food truck features recipes that are based on their parent's old Texas recipes with a California twist! It's In The Sauce BBQ is known for their Tri-Tip Sandwich, but offers many tasty items including everything from BBQ hamburgers and Pulled Pork Sandwiches to Breakfast Burritos and Cheesy Potatoes.
name: It's In The Sauce BBQ
